# --- WHT codec: NEVER commit the algorithm source ---
# The patented algorithm (AU 2026901656 / 2026901657) is the Phase-4 prize.
# Only the compiled .so / .pyd / .dylib ships publicly.
brain/_wht_core.pyx
brain/_wht_core.c
brain/_build/
*.pyx
!brain/sensor_wht.py

# Protected backup (if you ever keep a copy locally, don't push it)
_wht_source_PROTECTED/
